 26+  0000              TXAREAPX       EQU     480             ; TEXT AREA WIDTH (80 × 6PX)
 27+  0000              TXORG_X         EQU     GUTL_PX         ; TEXT AREA X ORIGIN
 28+  0000              TXORG_Y         EQU     CELLH           ; TEXT AREA Y ORIGIN (SKIP MENU ROW 0)
