112+  0727
113+  0727              ; - EXPNORM ----------
114+  0727              ; - EXPAND ONE 1BPP ROM ROW BYTE TO 2-BYTE VRAM ROW (NORMAL, SCREEN 6 2BPP)
115+  0727              ; - A:  ROM ROW BYTE (BITS 7-2 = 6 PIXELS)
116+  0727              ; - DE: DESTINATION VRAM ROW BUFFER (2 BYTES)
117+  0727              ; -
118+  0727
119+  0727 C5           EXPNORM         PUSH    BC
